The Herald On Wednesday Zimbabweans celebrated the commissioning of Marovanyati Dam in Manicaland Province. The infrastructure is going to transform the development landscape and lives of thousands of rural residents in this part of the country. Buhera District, where the newly commissioned dam is, suffers from low rainfall, perennially, and is susceptible to the vagaries of the weather. Joining the celebrations on Wednesday was young Lyzette Munzveda a Grade Five pupil from Chapanduka Primary School, Buhera. She had her own unique way of celebrating the development, described as a game-changer for the district. Her poem, celebrating commissioning of the dam, earned her support of President Mnangagwa, who gave her USD$100 and pledged support for her school fees until she completes her university studies. Here is the poem that transformed the course of Lyzette Munzveda’s life: Ndinokutendai Ichokwadi,  Idi chairo Apa ndipo pamakabaya dede nomukanwa Vakanga vazviona zvokunaka kwechakanaka Ndokushaya romuromo, pashure ndokuti Chakanaka chakanaka, mukaka haurungwi munyu  Ndinokutendai Kunaka kwemvura, ini ndinokuziva Haungaribiki rikadyika, Mvura pasina Verukanda rwemvura kumenyukira uko Imvura, Izvo Zviri pachena semhuno Jenaguru chairo kukosha kwemvura Muneenyu matundundu kuzere  Pano paMarovanyati raiva renje kareko Vaitambura vana vevanhu, pokuwana Raive dambudziko remoyo Ndangariro neshungu zvichiita kupingirishana Zvipfuyo chaizvo, zvikara zvesango, zvaita Kurezurwa nenyota  Mukuru wenyika, His Excellency, Cde E D Mnangagwa, Pamwechete navanamazvikokota Mhindimbi mukurima, vakaisa misoro pamwe Ndokundiparurira chino chirongwa  Kudzikamisa nekusimudzira zvizvarwa Muno muBuhera District kunyanya Pano paMarovanyati vakange vazviona Kuti mvura kumberi Vakange vazviona kuti Mvura inokosha Ichokwadi simba rehove riri mumvura Ndizvo ndizvo newe murimi  Haiwa zvatinakira pano paMarovanyati Mhururu nemuridzo uko- o Apa kwangova kukurumai nzeve  Mukuru wenyika wakashanda nevarimi Kwenguva zvirongwa nezvirongwa zvichiparurwa Mbeu dzichipiwa pachena, zvidzidzo nezvidzidzo Pfumvudza nhasi, iri kupisa mbeu ichipiwa pachena Ndinokutendai  Basa riri pano paMarovanyati iri Rinonongedza rutivirutivi achinongedza Makaita basa. Idi kutenda kwekitsi kuri mumpoyo  His Excellency, Cde E D Mnangagwa Tinokupai sando dzenyu, kusimudzira nyika Zvinemutsindo, penyu makasakura mazivisa Vene venzvimbo ino makandwa muupfu  Kukohwa Mvura kukohwa upfumi Chikonzero, kurima kunoda Mvura  Zvipfuyo zvinomwa, vanhu nezvimwewo Zvipukanana zvesango ndaramo yazvo Inobva pamvura Mukuru wenyika kutivhurira mikana Yemadiridziro kititendera tirime patinodira Pachena sezvatinoda, nguva dzose  SekuBuhera  District, taburwa mumoto Musenga wazvose kusumudzira nyika Yedu yeZimbabwe, mukurima kuri kwose zvako  Pano paMarovanyatitiri Kunyundumiswa nemafaro Mukurongwa kwazvo vamwe vaiti totenda damwa Zvadzamwa nhasi cahati regai tione Kunowira tsvimbo nedohwe  Inyasha guhwa kuperekedza wanyumwa Heuno mukana werakajeka ramangwana Tapinda tapinda mushuviro dzemoyo Timhanyidzane varimi pakurima upfumi hurimuvhu  Kuvarimi zvinhu zviedwa chembere yekwa Chivi Yakabika mabwe ndokunwa muto Matanda mazununguswa imi mosiya Nerakaorera, nyamba karekare hakana nyakuona Munyu ngwarirai Nokuti Ndakaziva hwutungamiri  Saka tiri pano paMarovanyati Semurau wemafaro tichidya nekunwa Kutatajura nokutatajura kunyanduka nokunyanduka Pachena, kupembenuka, kurandanuka, kutandavara Kupuranyemba nemusana muneyedu Zimbabwe Izere rusununguko, Garwe riri tii Iwe woshora rusununguko rwakadai Kusatenda pakadai uroyi